#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"# pcs status\n"
"Last updated: Fri Sep 14 09:52:25 2012\n"
"Last change: Fri Sep 14 09:51:55 2012 via crmd on pcmk-2\n"
"Stack: corosync\n"
"Current DC: pcmk-2 (2) - partition with quorum\n"
